Although I have no criminal record, I humbly request that the court consider the mitigating factor of my guilty plea. By pleading guilty, I express my remorse and demonstrate my willingness to accept the consequences of my actions. I am devoted to embracing the necessary measures to ensure that I never find myself in a similar situation again.

